{"tid":637362,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲都好想快啲報答到屋企","createTime":"2018-04-21T17:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T13:51:00.000Z","uid":22375,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"85965f5a6ae4691f6aac8618183088b75e704ecb","tid":637362,"uid":22375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:29:45.000Z","msg":"大學畢業左一段時間<br />\n仲未有一份好穩定既工作 可以令自己同父母都自豪<br />\n覺得自己係可以更加好<br />\n慢慢 係人生路上好似被初初既中學 大學同學超過<br />\n大家都有好既愛侶 鍾意既工作 好既理想<br />\n最近計劃轉工既時候 面對住一大堆公司名同數字<br />\n個人更加大壓力<br />\n我唔係想逃避.. 但要係翻工既時間做好工作 放工又唔敢同屋企人提起 <br />\n積累之下想分擔呢份攰既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好想快點再出發<br />\n希望自己唔開心一陣之後 <br />\n就加油 俾心機向前行<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fde80f9cdf4052cf625e03216bf5eb9e6bb6d9","tid":637362,"uid":127116,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T18:03:11.000Z","msg":"巴打加油<br />\n有咩想發洩就呢到講啦<br />\n大把人聽你講<br />\n堅持住啊你"},{"pid":"c9a7a992db6fde40aad4617c68f8485c884638c8","tid":637362,"uid":22375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5fde80f9cdf4052cf625e03216bf5eb9e6bb6d9","tid":637362,"uid":127116,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T18:03:11.000Z","msg":"巴打加油<br />\n有咩想發洩就呢到講啦<br />\n大把人聽你講<br />\n堅持住啊你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T18:04:22.000Z","msg":"多謝你好好<br />\n我地一齊加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c799ba730a8f475bec7162af82b8d3784776a3","tid":637362,"uid":41737,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T18:05:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c8be0019be9894b7a10babd16092b58180053e5","tid":637362,"uid":22375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3c799ba730a8f475bec7162af82b8d3784776a3","tid":637362,"uid":41737,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T18:05:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T18:09:13.000Z","m